@startuml
' @id(DOM-SESSION-CONTEXT)
' @desc(DOM-SESSION-CONTEXT, "Built as the SessionContext struct in crates/mdd-core/src/lib.rs: { toc: Vec<TocEntry>, fresh: bool, source_revision: Option<String>, drift: Vec<MapDrift> }. TocEntry is { kind: String, concept_count: usize, id_count: usize }. Returned by Project::session_context; the fresh/drift/source_revision fields are copied from MapStatusReport so the brief and `mdd map-status` never disagree.")
' @id(DOM-MAP-BASELINE)
' @desc(DOM-MAP-BASELINE, "Built as Project::read_map_source_revision + Project::derive_map_baseline in crates/mdd-core/src/lib.rs. An explicit non-empty source_revision in .mdd/map/manifest.yml wins; otherwise derive_map_baseline runs `git log -1 --format=%H -- .mdd/models/current` (the last commit touching the current diagrams). No .mdd/map manifest -> None (FRESH, no baseline). Nothing is written; the baseline self-maintains off commit history.")
' @id(DOM-SESSION-HOOK)
' @desc(DOM-SESSION-HOOK, "The mdd-managed SessionStart entry { type: command, command: \"mdd context\" } (templates::SESSION_HOOK_COMMAND). upsert_session_hook merges it into .claude/settings.json keyed by command (idempotent); strip_session_hook removes exactly it and prunes emptied groups/keys; command_hook_matches / group_has_command are the matchers. Driven by Project::write_session_hook (init) and Project::remove_session_hook (clean).")
' Current-side domain model for agent session bootstrap (cycle 0014), as built.
title Agent session bootstrap — domain (current)

class SessionContext <<value>> {
  + toc : TocEntry[]
  + fresh : boolean
  + source_revision : String [0..1]
  + drift : MapDrift[]
}

class TocEntry <<value>> {
  + kind : String
  + concept_count : int
  + id_count : int
}

class MapBaseline <<value>> {
  + explicit : Revision [0..1]
  + resolve() : Revision [0..1]
}

class SessionHook <<value>> {
  + event : "SessionStart"
  + type : "command"
  + command : "mdd context"
}

SessionContext "1" o-- "*" TocEntry
SessionContext ..> MapBaseline : freshness via map_status

note right of MapBaseline
  resolve() = read_map_source_revision: explicit
  source_revision, else derive_map_baseline
  (git log over .mdd/models/current). None when
  no whole-map manifest exists.
end note

note bottom of SessionHook
  upsert_session_hook / strip_session_hook on
  .claude/settings.json. Idempotent, keyed by command.
end note
@enduml
